content.body: Can’t wait to see some of you tomorrow! Meysam should be expecting us around 9am at the Google office (I think one of the invites said 8). I’ll be there but I think timing is a bit flexible so just message if you need to be let in later!
I'll be coming in later in the day (probably mid day) as my flight is in the morning tomorrow.
I just got into Munich! See you all soon
